      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. This is a distinguished opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking a specimen that remains in showroom state. Experience uncompromising quality and mechanical excellence in this peerless offering.",
