    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to come see this absolute beauty. I have babied this car since the day I got it, and it's still in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
